snippet.title: Zombies Monsters Robots - Closed Beta 2 Trailer
snippet.description:
ZMR closed beta 2 is LIVE! 

Get your own code from one of our partners: http://goo.gl/V6xKuW

Make every shot count as you enter a war against infectious zombies, abominable monsters, and murderous robots that will stop at nothing to see the end of mankind. This is the world of ZMR.
